column2: SELECT x.MatchID, x.RA, x.Dec,         m.ID, m.ra, m.dec,        s.objID, s.ra, s.dec, s.u, s.g, s.r, s.i, s.z INTO MYDB:xmatchtable FROM XMATCH (         MUST EXIST IN MYDB:webuser.radec2 AS m WITH(POINT(ra, dec), ERROR(#)),        MUST EXIST IN SDSSDR1#:Galaxy AS s WITH(ERROR(RaErr, #, #))        LIMIT BAYESFACTOR TO #) AS x      INNER JOIN SDSSDR1#:SpecObj sp ON sp.bestObjID = s.objID
